                    "description": "Supply Today supports companies and their employees with future proof supply chain solutions. As end-to and partner we assist in every part of the transformation process. \n\nFor more than 30 years we help retailers and producers to grow and to accelerate their growth.\n\nTogether with our customers we develop supply chain strategies to facilitate growth, to increase product availability and to realise low costs. Supply Today develops network infrastructures, designs logistics lay-outs, production lay-outs and warehouse buildings. We investigate investments scenarios to support the transformation. Our designs include the latest mechanisations solutions.\n\nIn addition to the design we also implement. Whether it is developing and building a turn key warehouse, integrating logistics operations or implementing new mechanised operational systems. Supply Today has the experienced managers who takes control and supports you in reaching your targets within the set time and budget frame. \n\nApart from designing and implementing new operations we also assist in seeking opportunities in existing processes. Areas of substantial potential are among others mechanisation of current operations, implementing new warehouse management systems, increasing visibility and redefining roles and responsibilities in supply chains or aligning sales and operations planning processes.\nWe have in-depth knowledge of selecting and implementing WMS and solver tools and are highly experienced in tender- and contract management for transport, warehousing and shipping.",
